<h1>Overlay legacy-audio - Legacy audio tools and samples</h1>
<p>Provides the legacy audio commands
<code>audioconvert</code>,
<code>audioctl</code>,
<code>audioplay</code>,
and <code>audiorecord</code>.
</p>
<p>Also provides the sample audio files which you'll find in the
<code>/usr/share/audio/samples/au</code> directory.</p>
